    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay acetaminophen sounds safer. how much of the acetaminophen can i take with the warfarin? like is there a specific dose i should stick to so it doesn't interact or something? i just want to make sure i take enough to actually kill this headache without making things complicated.",
